---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About"
  description="David Farley — 30-year finance and automation veteran. From advanced Excel and VBA solutions to enterprise RPA, he's been automating business processes his entire career."
  heroTitle="An Operations Team That Builds Automation"
  heroSubtitle="We have lived your processes. Now we automate them."
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Background -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Background</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          ForgeRPA was founded on a simple observation: the people who understand business processes best are rarely the ones building the automations. That gap leads to solutions that look good in demos but fall apart in production.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Our founder, David Farley, spent 30 years in finance and operations leadership — Controller, Finance Manager, Senior Accountant — across industries. He turned that operational knowledge into an automation practice. From advanced Excel and VBA in the early days to enterprise RPA and AI-powered process conversion today, he has architected and deployed hundreds of automations across industries. They work because they were designed by someone who has actually done the work.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          David has sat in the Controller's chair. He has closed the books every month. He has lived the pain of manual processes, reconciliation errors, and month-end crunch. That firsthand experience is what drives every automation we build.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          ForgeRPA exists because every company deserves access to enterprise-grade automation. Without the enterprise price tag.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Credentials -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Credentials</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📜</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal">CPA Background</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Controller, Finance Manager, and other<br />leadership roles across industries</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🤖</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal">UiPath Certified</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Certified UiPath Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Achievements -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Track Record</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {[
            { metric: 'Significant cost savings', context: 'Built custom systems that transformed manual operations into automated workflows, delivering measurable ROI across multiple engagements.' },
            { metric: 'Hundreds of enterprise automations deployed', context: '30 years of business process automation. From advanced Excel and VBA solutions to enterprise RPA, deployed across industries.' },
            { metric: 'Month-end close acceleration', context: 'Proven track record of significantly reducing close timelines across multiple companies.' },
            { metric: 'Workday iLoad conversions at scale', context: 'Managed and executed data conversions across multiple Workday implementations using dozens of pre-built templates.' },
            { metric: '"Silver Bullet" recognition', context: 'Recognized for automation solutions that resolved long-standing operational challenges.' },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-amber rounded-full mt-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal text-lg">{item.metric}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.context}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Philosophy -->
      <div class="mb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-charcoal-light rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber mb-4">Philosophy</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic">
          "You get someone who has lived your processes — closed the books, managed the team, fought the fires — and then learned to automate all of it. Every automation we build starts with the question: does this make business sense? If the ROI does not clear the hurdle rate, we do not build it."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Industries -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Industries Served</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Manufacturing', 'Financial Services', 'Insurance', 'Restaurant & Hospitality', 'Professional Services', 'Healthcare', 'Technology', 'Automotive'].map((industry) => (
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark font-medium rounded-lg text-sm">
              {industry}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm">These are a few of the industries we have worked in. Our approach applies to any industry with manual processes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    heading="Let's Talk About Your Processes"
    subtext="30 minutes. No sales pitch. Just an honest conversation about where automation can make the biggest impact for your team."
    ctaText="Book a Discovery Call"
    ctaLink="/contact"
  />
</PageLayout>
